KCPE and KCSE exam candidates will sit their exams under under strict rules issued by Education CS Fred Matiang i (pictured). Preparations for the two national exams in Bunyala subcounty are complete.Director of education Francis Ochieng said invigilators for 37 primary school and 11 secondary school centres have been given clear instructions so they can prevent any cheating. He said stern action will be taken against violators.